nodes.text: Dorrel was a male Bith Jedi Master stationed on Hoth during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire.

Dorrel appears in the appears in the game files for Star Wars: The Old Republic under the mission Subzero Emergency. The mission and Dorrel were cut before release. Dorrel's species and the mission he was set to appear in can be found on Jedipedia.
